Package de.dedede.model.data.dtos

Class UserDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.dedede.model.data.dtos.UserDto
  • public class UserDto
extends java.lang.Object
    This DTO (data transfer object) is responsible for aggregating and encapsulating data about a user for transfer.

    See the UserDao class to which this DTO is passed.

    Author:
    Sergei Pravdin
